Version 1.0.3 (Mar 23 2001)
* Portability fix for Solaris
* Separated scores and word list updates
* Decreased minimum game delay

Version 1.0.2 (Mar 15 2001)
* Each dictionary gets equal space in the high score table
* Better Curses detection
* Tidied cursor handling when invisible cursors not supported, and other
  misc cosmetic fixes
* Increased high score table to 20 entries

Version 1.0.1 (Feb 15 2001)
* Added next letter to score display
* Added dictionary name sanity check
* Minor cosmetic changes

Version 1.0 (Feb 14 2001)
* First public release.
